description:
A Dark theme for "Minimal 1.0" designed by me.

Theme can be found here - http://tinyurl.com/37felak

Known bugs - Does cover glass correctly in maximized mode, Small graphical issues when using alt to show menus.

/*==DESIGNED BY WARBOY FROM NEOWIN==*/
/*++Use with the Firefox 4.0 "Minimal 1.0" Theme by SoapyHamHocks and BoneyardBrew++*/
/*--Known bugs - Does not cover glass correctly in maximized mode, Small graphical issues when using alt to show menus, The New Tab Button does not work correctly using this version. Will fix in future revision. Tab close button does not work correctly, Not my fault.--*/

css:
/*==DESIGNED BY WARBOY FROM NEOWIN==*/
/*++Use with the Firefox 4.0 "Minimal 1.0" Theme by SoapyHamHocks and BoneyardBrew++*/
/*--Known bugs - Does not cover glass correctly in maximized mode, Small graphical issues when using alt to show menus, The New Tab Button does not work correctly using this version. Will fix in future revision. Tab close button does not work correctly, Not my fault.--*/

#appmenu-button .button-text{
color: transparent !important;
text-shadow: none !important;
margin-left: -15px !important;
margin-right: -15px !important;
}

#appmenu-button > .button-box:after{
 content: "Darkfox" !important;
 padding: 0 0px 0 0px !important;
 text-shadow: 0 0px 2px rgba(0,0,0,2), 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0,1) !important;
}

#appmenu-button{
/*-moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;*/
background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, rgba(80,80,120,.7), rgba(0,0,0,.7)) !important;
-moz-border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px !important;
border-top: 0px !important;
margin-top: -1px !important;
min-width: 95px !important;
width: 95px !important;
}

#appmenu-button:hover{
background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, rgba(33,170,222,.8), rgba(25,62,118,.8)) !important;
}

#navigator-toolbox[tabsontop="true"] #TabsToolbar{
padding-bottom: 0px !important;
padding-left: 0px !important;
margin-right: 101px !important;
}

#nav-bar:-moz-system-metric(windows-default-theme){
  -moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;
padding-bottom: 1px !important;
padding-top: 0px !important;
}

.tabbrowser-tabs{
-moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;
margin-top: -7px !important; 
margin-left: -11px !important;
}

.tabbrowser-tab .tab-text{
color: -moz-win-mediatext !important;
}

statusbarpanel{
-moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;
color: -moz-win-mediatext !important;
}

#FindToolbar{ 
-moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;
color: -moz-win-mediatext !important;
}

.tabbrowser-tab:hover{
background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, rgba(33,170,222,.9), rgba(25,62,118,.9)) !important;
}

.tabbrowser-tab:not([selected="true"]) {
background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.5) !important;
}

#PersonalToolbar{
border: 0 !important;
-moz-appearance: -moz-win-media-toolbox !important;
color: -moz-win-mediatext !important;
}
